{"type": "article", "id": 52267, "title": "辛芷蕾代言卡地亚腕表，百事可乐日本广告挺酷 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-04-18T04:05:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 49446, "name": "辛芷蕾"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 3790, "name": "卡地亚"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 106, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180418114922XeU4BOTiqPoEfvcF.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/44127\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>辛芷蕾代言卡地亚新款腕表 Panthèrede Cartier</b></a>，并出演了一支微电影广告《豹姿魅影》，成为鹿晗、邓超、马思纯之后第四位中国市场的品牌挚友。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=w0631do0egm&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NDAwMDk4MA==&amp;mid=2668035842&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b346b973f1325881a3cd4a16e82cd689&amp;chksm=bc7c26398b0baf2fe666f4d859b5f782ebbcef234ad607e19ef10013f04907575bd2eaea6718&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0418IUxEaqQ7ksQtFskmk8hr&amp;key=81c79c138bc9861d5050137d5e11aba06b47eef4bd2b26a858fa105d234f7c7730230f1ab3bd635d38011d19c315bb0439d8621bab567bd6b360ee1ddfdffe8145fdba76afba50655d906de9d9a2bed1&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.13.4+build(17E199)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=%2B4rEJ9VyX5GVpul9CBQWqlqvn8%2FPYlew3wQ2oDdQ3LGGRJlriTU9an5CdATXZ7uq\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳 X 王者荣耀</b></a>：快餐巨头们还在寻找年轻人到店消费的理由……比如说，一起开黑。不过玩法还是推出多款合作产品、抽取游戏皮肤、赠送闪卡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=s0631ntbxtv&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26678.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天天爱消除 X 奥利奥</b></a>：爱消除里的萌物们出演了奥利奥的最新广告，一起参观了奥利奥巨大的音乐戈德堡装置，这是奥利奥最新推出的音乐盒营销。制作公司是&nbsp;Amused Art。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0539a1ut6l&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2018/4/nasa-vans-old-skool\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Twitter 上曝光了一款 VANS 与美国国家航空航天局 NASA 合作的联名鞋款</b></a>。鞋款以 Old Skool 作为鞋型基底，鞋部测沿出带有 NASA 专属标志以及航空局的坐标地点。据说除此以外也有 Hi-Top 等其他鞋款，将于 10 月 1 日发布。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418105829WDIJCpE7qUPvFozY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666972\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/45163.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>苹果在日本开了第一家采用“城市广场”概念的商店</b></a>，新宿店的霓虹 LOGO 一反过往的苹果设计风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418115008tGfvbVRlH28AQdei.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564063\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418110703joBlZ6ezG8TJK2VQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552511\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418110712Ifj1lBWaV8uRPZGo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26731.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>无印良品给 2018 春夏系列的亚麻服饰拍摄了一支广告</b></a>，整支视频没有任何剧情和人物，只是单纯拍摄亚麻衬衫在风中的律动，配乐和画风都延续了 MUJ I一贯清淡的风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=n0610okk0qt&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/44121\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百事可乐日本发布了广告《怪物舞踏団》</b></a>，把传统的祭祀的形式和舞蹈结合电吉他等重金属乐器，配合石川小百合的歌声，宛若百鬼夜行主题的演唱会。糅合了日本传统与现代的因素，是很有特色的本土化营销。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0631u625ml&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/44123\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宝马 mini 系列一直深受女性消费者的喜爱，为了打开男性消费者市场，宝马将产品重新定位“迷你象征着力量”。</b></a>波兰经销商邀请美国橄榄球联盟教练 Craig Parkinson 作为“迷你象征着力量”活动的代表，并发布一支广告。<br></p><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=c06311dsgtw&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><b>万宝龙为大班系列小王子特别版制作了一个 H5 动画广告，</b><a href=\"http://llp.montblanc.cn/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">点击这里试玩<span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54);\">。</span></a><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418111211zYCwjipBnvUeFk6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180418111243lfqhvxDXaG6kSyLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26718.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为了推销自家的防晒产品</b></a>，自然堂找了郑恺到紫外线高强度的喜马拉雅接受连续 72 小时的暴晒挑战，并拍摄了 9 段视频。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=i0631p4fjin&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\">题图来源：百事可乐</p>"}